-diff/assets/fixtures/onboarding-before.md\n41: .opencode/commands/create/diff.md\n42: .claude/commands/create/diff.md\n43: .opencode/commands/create/README.txt\n44: .opencode/skills/sk-doc/SKILL.md\n45: .opencode/commands/create/assets/create_diff_auto.yaml\n46: .opencode/commands/create/assets/create_diff_confirm.yaml\n47: .opencode/commands/create/assets/create_diff_presentation.txt\n\n(End of file - total 47 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Review scope for the create-diff deep review: skill tree, command surface, hub routing.\n# One repo-relative path per line; consumed by deep-review scope discovery.\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/README.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/SKILL.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/feature-catalog/feature-catalog.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/feature-catalog/snapshot-lifecycle/baseline-snapshot-and-compare.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/feature-catalog/snapshot-lifecycle/snapshot-state-management.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/feature-catalog/snapshot-lifecycle/explicit-pair-comparison.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/feature-catalog/comparison-engine/deterministic-diffing.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/feature-catalog/comparison-engine/self-contained-report.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/feature-catalog/comparison-engine/multi-format-extraction.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/feature-catalog/safety-and-capabilities/capability-tier-reporting.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/feature-catalog/safety-and-capabilities/report-safety-validation.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/changelog/v1.1.0.0.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/references/capabilities-and-fidelity.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/references/workflow.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/references/worked-example.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-diff/references/README.md\n.opencode/skills/sk-do