{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784210795870,"sessionID":"ses_094c57e18ffemFIYitl0QMkdbq","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_HCTKC6CwuKwfyygb437AbMC2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/033-create-diff-mode/010-fluid-responsive-report/review/lineages/sol/deep-review-strategy.md","offset":1,"limit":230},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/033-create-diff-mode/010-fluid-responsive-report/review/lineages/sol/deep-review-strategy.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Deep Review Strategy - Fluid Responsive Report\n2: \n3: ## 1. TOPIC\n4: Review `.opencode/specs/sk-doc/033-create-diff-mode/010-fluid-responsive-report` and the 45 files declared by its `goal-file-manifest.txt`.\n5: \n6: ## 2. REVIEW CHARTER\n7: - Target: completed Level 2 spec packet and its declared create-diff implementation, documentation, command, catalog, and playbook surfaces.\n8: - Dimensions: correctness, security, traceability, maintainability.\n9: - Core protocols: `spec_code`, `checklist_evidence`.\n10: - Applicable overlays: `feature_catalog_code`, `playbook_capability`.\n11: - Resource Map Coverage: `resource-map.md` not present; skipping coverage gate.\n12: \n13: ## 3. REVIEW DIMENSIONS (remaining)\n14: <!-- ANCHOR:review-dimensions -->\n15: ## 3. REVIEW DIMENSIONS (remaining)\n16: - [ ] correctness\n17: - [ ] maintainability\n18: \n19: <!-- /ANCHOR:review-dimensions -->\n20: \n21: ## 4. NON-GOALS\n22: - Implementing fixes or changing any target file.\n23: - Expanding review beyond the manifest, canonical packet documents, and directly named evidence.\n24: - Performing subjective live IDE-webview acceptance that requires an operator runtime.\n25: \n26: ## 5. STOP CONDITIONS\n27: - Legal convergence after all dimensions and core protocols are covered and stabilized, or iteration 10.\n28: - Any termi